title: Beautiful Icon Styler v1.0.7 [Full].apk
description:
Beautiful Icon Styler enables you to apply 3rd party icon themes to home screen icons in stock launchers.

No root required.

The app can only style the home screen icons, icons in app drawer stay original.

Supported home apps:
- Stock Android Launcher
- Google Now Launcher
- Samsung Home (TouchWiz)
- Motorola Homescreen
- HTC Sense Homescreen
- LG Homescreen

Supported icon packs:
Apex/Nova compatible icon packs
